titles.title: An original resolution to authorize the printing of a revised edition of the Senate Election Law Guidebook.

calendar.text: Committee on Rules ordered to be reported an original measure.

action.text: Committee on Rules. Original measure reported to Senate by Senator Ford. Without written report.

calendar.text: Placed on Senate Legislative Calendar under General Orders. Calendar No. 267.

vote.text: Resolution agreed to in Senate without amendment by Voice Vote. (consideration: CR 11/10/93 S15638)

bill.summary: 11/4/1993--Introduced. Directs the Senate Committee on Rules and Administration to prepare a revised edition of the Senate Election Law Guidebook to be printed as a Senate document.
